вҹҰ Test that helper functions are now allowed вҹ§

вҹҰ Utility function used by multiple functions вҹ§
О»isPositive(x:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=x>0

О»main()вҶ’рқ•Ҡ=processA(50)++" and "++processB(-5)

О»processA(x:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ•Ҡ match isPositive(x){
  trueвҶ’"positive"|
  falseвҶ’"negative"
}

О»processB(y:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ•Ҡ match isPositive(y){
  trueвҶ’"yes"|
  falseвҶ’"no"
}
